[R2] M.Rashid , “Microelectronic Circuit”, Cengage Learning Publication.
[R3] Sedra & Smith, “Micro Electronic Circuits” Oxford University Press, 2000
[R4] David A Bell, “Operational Amplifiers and Linear IC’s”, PHI.